{"tid":2263453,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"等𨋢聽到入面有人聲","createTime":"2020-10-30T02:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T17:04:10.000Z","uid":58391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9910b17e341589f2753e5d1330d255fecbbab819","tid":2263453,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"我見架𨋢係我禁完先喺地下上黎<br />\n隨即就聽到有一個小朋友同一個女人喺𨋢度傳出黎<br />\n佢地講咩我都好清楚聽到 我以為佢地咁岩喺地下果層入𨋢<br />\n但d聲又冇理由咁近 我住20樓 架𨋢只係行到1,2樓 <br />\n直程係近到隔住對𨋢門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開門冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都試過聽到有個阿叔喺度講野 以為佢冇禁樓層唔小心上左黎 <br />\n但𨋢到又冇人喺度<br />\n請問係咪物理現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知邊度反彈d聲入𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3ad863e2c0c5fee0568e35131e0d97d107b3c4","tid":2263453,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:11:20.000Z","msg":"入𨋢之後望下頭頂"},{"pid":"4086f7bd68d376dfd3a9648afaf1c70cc24990ce","tid":2263453,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"你望下上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609c465ed6104ebc76def295f8bf0d5407ee9ad8","tid":2263453,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3ad863e2c0c5fee0568e35131e0d97d107b3c4","tid":2263453,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:11:20.000Z","msg":"入𨋢之後望下頭頂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"認真有望過 冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4aec60fc0d86d0c8bd0c79da34ad5de3ea8d0e","tid":2263453,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4086f7bd68d376dfd3a9648afaf1c70cc24990ce","tid":2263453,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:11